reviewText: love it, its my favorite show
It is entertaining and doesn't get bore watching  them all over again.

My wife got me to watch some of the episodes of this TV series from the Philippines.  I truly enjoyed the quality.  The writers are very good and it is fun to watch.  She told me that it is one of the top three TV series in the Philippines.  I would like to tell you a short summary but I would just ruin it for you.  Buy the episodes that you missed or the whole series.  I expect additional volumes to be sold and hopefully, it will be on Amazon.  Thank you.
